description:
Runs OpenGL ES content on Windows by translating OpenGL ES API calls to DirectX 11 API calls.
Targets Universal Windows 10 apps (UWP). See 'ANGLE.WindowsStore' for non-ARM64 apps.
title: Servo's fork of ANGLE for Windows Store (UWP)
